{"tha-ap6:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap6:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap6:0.3":"Anuruddhattheraapadana ","tha-ap6:1.1":"â€œSumedham bhagavantaham, ","tha-ap6:1.2":"lokajettham narasabham; ","tha-ap6:1.3":"Vupakattham viharantam, ","tha-ap6:1.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap6:2.1":"Upagantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap6:2.2":"sumedham lokanayakam; ","tha-ap6:2.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap6:2.4":"buddhasetthamayacaham. ","tha-ap6:3.1":"Anukampa mahavira, ","tha-ap6:3.2":"lokajettha narasabha; ","tha-ap6:3.3":"Padipam te padassami, ","tha-ap6:3.4":"rukkhamulamhi jhayato. ","tha-ap6:4.1":"Adhivasesi so dhiro, ","tha-ap6:4.2":"sayambhu vadatam varo; ","tha-ap6:4.3":"Dumesu vinivijjhitva, ","tha-ap6:4.4":"yantam yojiyaham tada. ","tha-ap6:5.1":"Sahassavattim padasim, ","tha-ap6:5.2":"buddhassa lokabandhuno; ","tha-ap6:5.3":"Sattaham pajjalitvana, ","tha-ap6:5.4":"dipa vupasamimsu me. ","tha-ap6:6.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap6:6.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap6:6.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap6:6.4":"vimanamupapajjaham. ","tha-ap6:7.1":"Upapannassa devattam, ","tha-ap6:7.2":"byamham asi sunimmitam; ","tha-ap6:7.3":"Samantato pajjalati, ","tha-ap6:7.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap6:8.1":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","tha-ap6:8.2":"virocesimaham tada; ","tha-ap6:8.3":"Sabbe deve abhibhomi, ","tha-ap6:8.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap6:9.1":"Timsakappani devindo, ","tha-ap6:9.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap6:9.3":"Na mam kecitimannanti, ","tha-ap6:9.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap6:10.1":"Atthavisatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap6:10.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap6:10.3":"Diva rattinca passami, ","tha-ap6:10.4":"samanta yojanam tada. ","tha-ap6:11.1":"Sahassalokam nanena, ","tha-ap6:11.2":"passami satthu sasane; ","tha-ap6:11.3":"Dibbacakkhumanuppatto, ","tha-ap6:11.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap6:12.1":"Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap6:12.2":"timsakappasahassito; ","tha-ap6:12.3":"Tassa dipo maya dinno, ","tha-ap6:12.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap6:13.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap6:13.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap6:13.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap6:13.4":"katam buddhassa sasanamâ€. ","tha-ap6:14.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma anuruddho thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap6:15.1":"Anuruddhattherassapadanam catuttham. "}